    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>With the Linear integration, HackerOne makes it easy for you to track Linear issues as references on the platform. Linear only supports directly linking to the issue creation form on a per-project basis, so if you use multiple projects, there currently isn’t a good way of pre-filling data as a report could affect different projects. If most of your reports only affect one project, issue creation can be much easier.</p>\n<p>In order to configure the Linear integration for your team, <a href=\"https://support.hackerone.com/hc/en-us/requests/new\">contact HackerOne</a> with the following information:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The linear project name</li>\n</ul>\n<p>With the provided information, HackerOne will be able to set up your requested integration. You’ll get an email notification letting you know that your integration has been set up within 1-2 business days.</p>\n<h3 id=\"how-the-integration-works\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-the-integration-works\" aria-label=\"how the integration works permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How the Integration Works</h3>\n<p>After your Linear integration has been set up:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Click <strong>Edit</strong> next to the <strong>References</strong> field.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Edit References\"\n        title=\"Edit References\"\n        src=\"/static/ecaf12c461e240847c5caa95c1c0c87d/0b533/github-11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ecaf12c461e240847c5caa95c1c0c87d/fac75/github-11.png 125w,\n/static/ecaf12c461e240847c5caa95c1c0c87d/63868/github-11.png 250w,\n/static/ecaf12c461e240847c5caa95c1c0c87d/0b533/github-11.png 500w,\n/static/ecaf12c461e240847c5caa95c1c0c87d/1f083/github-11.png 660w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Click <strong>Add reference to issue tracker</strong>.</li>\n<li>Make sure you select Manual integration is selected.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"integration\"\n        title=\"integration\"\n        src=\"/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/0b533/issue-tracker-reference.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/fac75/issue-tracker-reference.png 125w,\n/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/63868/issue-tracker-reference.png 250w,\n/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/0b533/issue-tracker-reference.png 500w,\n/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/1d69c/issue-tracker-reference.png 750w,\n/static/d2740c5ff2d72d3c3de3d733024a586d/63ec5/issue-tracker-reference.png 812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Click <strong>Generate escalation</strong>. You’ll be taken to your Linear account where the report is pre-populated.</li>\n<li>Submit the issue to create the report in Linear.</li>\n<li>Copy the Linear report issue number and paste it in the <strong>Reference ID</strong> field back in the HackerOne.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Create</strong> to create a direct reference link to the issue in Linear.</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"path":"/organizations/linear-integration.html","id":"organizations/linear-integration","title":"Linear Integration","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"How the Integration Works"}]}},"pageContext":{}},
